phrases.phrase: 늦게 배운 도둑이 날 새는 줄 모른다
meanings: A thief who has learned stealing later than others will not even realize that the day breaks while committing a theft

phrases.phrase: 늦게 시작한 도둑이 새벽 다 가는 줄 모른다
meanings: A thief who has learned stealing later than others will not even realize that the day breaks while committing a theft
